\p{Let #{X:\Comma{A}{\UU}} be a [reflection algebra](jms-003O); a \em{displayed reflection algebra} #{Y} over #{X} is defined to be a dependent type #{\bar{U}Y : X \to \UU} together with a dependent function #{\bar{\eta}\Sub{Y} : \Prod{a:A}{\bar{U}Y\prn{\eta\Sub{X}a}}.}}

\p{We will write #{Y[x]} for #{\bar{U}Yx}.}